messages.content: is israel part of the european economic area
No, Israel is not part of the European Economic Area.
is central bank of india a nationalised bank
Yes, it is a nationalized bank, meaning it is state-owned and operates under government regulations.
can you go out on a double in chicken foot
No, you're already on a date—call it an 'alone' date.
is in n out only located in california
No, while In-N-Out began in California, it has also expanded to other states including Nevada and Arizona.
is national and enterprise car rental the same company
No, National and Enterprise are separate entities, each with its own fleet and policies.
is copa airlines part of the star alliance
Yes, Copa Airlines is a member of the Star Alliance, enhancing its route offerings.
is health care free in the united states
No, in the US, healthcare is typically not free; it involves payments through insurance or out-of-pocket.
is an oz and a fl oz the same
No, an ounce is a weight measure, and a fluid ounce is a volume one, with fluid ounces being larger.
are all the angles equal in a parallelogram
No, a parallelogram has opposite angles that are equal, not all.
is the isle of man part of the european economic area
No, the Isle of Man is not part of the European Economic Area.
